title: Marilyn Manson - The Live Collection
description:
Here is a collection of all Live Songs released by Marilyn Manson (excluding The Last Tour On Earth EP). Tracks Ten and on are bonus. All are in mp3 format. Enjoy :)

1.Dried Up, Tied And Dead To The World [Live] (Remix & Repent EP)
2.Antichrist Superstar [Live] (Remix & Repent EP)
3.Sweet Dreams [Live] (The Dope Show Single)
4.Apple Of Sodom [Live] (The Dope Show Single)
5.The Beautiful People [Live] (The Dope Show Single)
6.The Fight Song [Live] (The Fight Song Single)
7.The Nobodies [Live In Denver] (The Nobodies Single)
8.The Death Song (With Bible Speech) [Live In Denver] (The Nobodies Single)
9.Mechanical Animals [Live] (Holy Wood Japan Bonus Track)
BONUS
10.Terrible Lie [Live]
11.Eye [Live feat. The Smashing Pumpkins]
12.The Beautiful People [Live feat. The Smashing Pumpkins]
13.The Dope Show [Live]
14.Sick City
15.Surrender [Live]
16.The Golden Age Of Grotesque [Live]
17.Heart-Shaped Glasses [Live]
18.What Goes Around Comes Around [Live]
